  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "The Nintendo DS version of Spider-Man 3, a videogame based on the 2007 movie of the same name.\n\nThe Nintendo DS version is completely 2.5D and uses the Touch Screen to execute most attacks. Players can put on the black suit at will, but it will be disabled if Spider-Man's health is too low. This version supports wireless multiplayer.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
